videos.description: Kyrie Irving puts up a heat check early as he pulls up from 31 feet away to splash down a deep 3-pointer from the AT&T Center logo in transition.

videos.description: Kyrie Irving wows everyone in traffic on the fast break as he throws an amazing yet subtle pass through his legs to Blake Griffin for the nice finish.
